Since $\angle ACB = 38^\circ$, \[\angle AIE = \frac{\angle BAC + \angle ABC}{2} = \frac{180^\circ - \angle ACB}{2} = \frac{180^\circ - 38^\circ}{2} = \boxed{71^\circ}.\]

